name: dbscan
description: An optimized implementation of the DBSCAN algorithm in C++. The grid-based approach is optimized using parallelism, including OpenMP, C++ Concurrency API, and work-stealing technique. AVX instructions are used to optimize floating-point arithmetic operations. The program achieves a 35.89x runtime improvement with 8 threads.
